## Turbo Drive

Turbo Drive automatically converts link clicks and form submissions into AJAX requests.

### How It Works

```erb
<!-- This link is automatically intercepted by Turbo Drive -->
<%= link_to "Articles", articles_path %>
<!-- Result: AJAX request, fast page transition, no full reload -->

<!-- This form is automatically handled by Turbo -->
<%= form_with model: @article do |f| %>
  <%= f.text_field :title %>
  <%= f.submit %>
<% end %>
<!-- Result: AJAX submission, page update without full reload -->
```

### Disabling Turbo Drive

```erb
<!-- Disable for specific links -->
<%= link_to "External Site", "https://example.com", data: { turbo: false } %>

<!-- Disable for forms that upload files -->
<%= form_with url: upload_path, data: { turbo: false } do |f| %>
  <%= f.file_field :document %>
  <%= f.submit %>
<% end %>
```

### Turbo Drive Benefits

- ✅ Faster page transitions
- ✅ Preserves scroll position
- ✅ Browser history works correctly
- ✅ No JavaScript needed (automatic)
